    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presented in collector-grade condition, this E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a GKN variable M-differential lock. Mechanical provenance is exhaustive, including recent valve clearance adjustments, preventative rod bearing replacement, and a fully reinforced rear subframe. The chassis remains rigid with original bushings and factory-spec dampers, while the exterior retains its original factory-spec depth and luster. Zero deferred maintenance; this is a turn-key example for the discerning driver who values mechanical transparency and structural integrity.",
